.gitignore
# Carve-outs: ship the bundled runner + its npm deps + the templates it
# resolves via __dirname. Without these the consumer-project fallback in
# packages/shared/src/status.ts:runLiveStatus has nothing to spawn.
!dist/runner/**
!dist/_templates/**
